  <p>
If [mathjaxinline]A[/mathjaxinline] is an [mathjaxinline]m\times n[/mathjaxinline] matrix </p>
  <table id="a0000000046" class="equation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="7" style="table-layout:auto">
    <tr>
      <td class="equation" style="width:80%;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;border-style:hidden">[mathjax]A = \left[ \begin{array}{cccc} | &amp;  | &amp; &amp;  | \\ v_1 &amp;  v_2 &amp;  \cdots &amp;  v_ n \\ | &amp;  | &amp; &amp;  | \end{array} \right],[/mathjax]</td>
